{"tid":1243687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫故知新]2012年民主黨投票支持「正式賦予駐港解放軍皇等權力」","createTime":"2019-06-19T14:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T18:15:21.000Z","uid":50275,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f285d23b57e7b9abd3c3dcde2b2f8147be86d9b3","tid":1243687,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/19/is7NPt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2Fis7NPt.jpg&h=91ff388d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.legcovotes.net/army/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legcovotes.net%2Farmy%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuyBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=c70afd49\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legcovotes.net/army/</a><br />\r\n<strong>官方名稱 : 法律適應化修改（軍事提述）條例草案<br />\r\n表決日期 :  2012年2月8日</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n條例生效後，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港法例任何條文的「<strong>英軍</strong>」字眼會改為「<strong>駐軍</strong>」；對<strong>女王陛下和皇室官方</strong>的提述，會改為<strong>中央人民政府</strong>；對<strong>皇室人員</strong>的豁免，亦會變成<strong>中央人民政府</strong>的豁免。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n殖民地時代派駐香港的英軍，和主權移交後中國派駐香港的駐軍，無論是性質和憲政地位上都有很大分別。但香港政府卻把舊時英軍的特權和豁免，逐項刻意保留下來給駐軍。更嚴重錯誤的是條例草案近乎機械式地把殖民地式的女王、官方所受的特權和豁免。改為中央官方，而刪除英國由豁免改為要受到法律制裁的部份。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n簡介<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/19/OSoZFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2FOSoZFt.jpg&h=a9b75155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n投票結果<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/19/OZqojC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2FOZqojC.jpg&h=ad89e6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n官方表決紀錄檔<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/19/3VWcDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F3VWcDA.jpg&h=f4ce950e&s={